A profile of Anthropic's Frontier Red Team, which is unique among AI companies in having a mandate to both evaluate its AI models and publicize findings widely (Sharon Goldman/Fortune)
Google now lets US-based Google Photos users turn static images into silent four-second videos using its Veo 3 model (Elissa Welle/The Verge)
Stripe and Paradigm unveil Tempo, a Layer-1 blockchain for stablecoins; a source says Tempo will not launch with its own token and there is no launch timeline (Leo Schwartz/Fortune)
